fields.Name: Get Typeform Responses
fields.Description: Retrieves responses from a Typeform with filtering, pagination, and search capabilities. Supports date ranges, completion status filters, and automatic pagination through all responses.

fields.Name: CompanyID
fields.Description: The MemberJunction Company ID for credential lookup (optional - defaults to user's company)

fields.Name: FormID
fields.Description: The Typeform form ID (found in the form URL)

fields.Name: PageSize
fields.Description: Number of responses per page (1-1000, default 25)

fields.Name: Since
fields.Description: Filter responses submitted since this date (ISO 8601 format or Unix timestamp)

fields.Name: Until
fields.Description: Filter responses submitted until this date (ISO 8601 format or Unix timestamp)

fields.Name: After
fields.Description: Response token for pagination - get next page after this token

fields.Name: Before
fields.Description: Response token for pagination - get page before this token

fields.Name: Completed
fields.Description: Filter by completion status (true=completed only, false=partial only, null=all)

fields.Name: Sort
fields.Description: Sort order: 'submitted_at,asc' or 'submitted_at,desc' (default: submitted_at,desc)

fields.Name: Query
fields.Description: Text search across all response answers

fields.Name: Fields
fields.Description: Comma-separated list of field IDs to include (returns only these fields)

fields.Name: GetAllPages
fields.Description: If true, automatically fetch all pages of responses (up to MaxResponses)

fields.Name: MaxResponses
fields.Description: Maximum number of responses to retrieve when GetAllPages is true (default 10000)

fields.Name: Responses
fields.Description: Array of response objects with all answers, metadata, and submission details

fields.Name: TotalItems
fields.Description: Total number of responses available matching the criteria

fields.Name: PageCount
fields.Description: Number of pages available

fields.Name: ResponseTokens
fields.Description: Object with 'before' and 'after' tokens for pagination

fields.Name: Count
fields.Description: Number of responses returned in this request
Responses retrieved successfully

fields.Name: FormID

fields.Name: ResponseToken

fields.Name: Response

fields.Name: ResponseID

fields.Name: SubmittedAt

fields.Name: Completed

fields.Name: Answers
fields.Description: Array of all answers with field IDs, questions, and values

fields.Name: Metadata
fields.Description: Browser, platform, referer, and user agent information

fields.Name: HiddenFields
fields.Description: Hidden field values passed via URL parameters

fields.Name: CalculatedFields
fields.Description: Calculated values like scores and completion time

fields.Name: Get Typeform Response Statistics
fields.Description: Calculates comprehensive statistics from Typeform responses including completion rates, response trends, popular answers, and time-based analytics. Useful for dashboards and reporting.

fields.Name: CompanyID
fields.Description: The MemberJunction Company ID for credential lookup (optional - defaults to user's company)

fields.Name: FormID
fields.Description: The Typeform form ID

fields.Name: Since
fields.Description: Start date for analysis (ISO 8601 format)

fields.Name: Until
fields.Description: End date for analysis (ISO 8601 format)

fields.Name: MaxResponses
fields.Description: Maximum responses to analyze (default 10000)

fields.Name: IncludeTopAnswers
fields.Description: Calculate most popular answers for each field (default true)

fields.Name: TopAnswersLimit
fields.Description: Number of top answers to return per field (default 10)

fields.Name: Statistics
fields.Description: Complete statistics object with all calculated metrics

fields.Name: TotalResponses
fields.Description: Total number of responses

fields.Name: CompletedResponses
fields.Description: Number of completed responses

fields.Name: PartialResponses
fields.Description: Number of partial/incomplete responses

fields.Name: CompletionRate
fields.Description: Percentage of responses that were completed

fields.Name: AverageCompletionTime
fields.Description: Average time to complete in seconds

fields.Name: ResponsesByDate
fields.Description: Daily breakdown of response counts

fields.Name: DailyBreakdown
fields.Description: Array of daily statistics with date, count, completed, and partial counts

fields.Name: HourlyDistribution
fields.Description: Array showing response distribution by hour of day (0-23)

fields.Name: TopAnswers

fields.Name: Watch for New Typeform Responses
fields.Description: Polls Typeform for new responses since the last check. Returns only new submissions and updates the last checked timestamp. Perfect for triggering workflows, sending notifications, or syncing data to other systems.

fields.Name: CompanyID
fields.Description: The MemberJunction Company ID for credential lookup (optional - defaults to user's company)

fields.Name: FormID
fields.Description: The Typeform form ID to monitor

fields.Name: LastCheckedTimestamp
fields.Description: ISO 8601 timestamp of last check. If not provided, uses DefaultLookbackMinutes.

fields.Name: DefaultLookbackMinutes
fields.Description: If LastCheckedTimestamp not provided, look back this many minutes (default 60)

fields.Name: OnlyCompleted
fields.Description: Only return completed responses (default false)

fields.Name: MaxResponses
fields.Description: Maximum new responses to return (default 1000)

fields.Name: NewResponses
fields.Description: Array of new responses since last check

fields.Name: NewResponseCount
fields.Description: Number of new responses found

fields.Name: CompletedCount
fields.Description: Number of completed responses in the new set

fields.Name: PartialCount
fields.Description: Number of partial responses in the new set

fields.Name: LastChecked
fields.Description: Updated timestamp to use for next check

fields.Name: PreviouslyChecked
fields.Description: The timestamp that was used for this check

fields.Name: ResponsesByType
fields.Description: Responses grouped by field type

fields.Name: ExtractedEmails
fields.Description: Email addresses extracted from responses

fields.Name: HasNewResponses
fields.Description: Boolean indicating if any new responses were found

fields.Name: Create Typeform
fields.Description: Creates a new Typeform with specified title, fields, and settings. Supports all field types including text, email, multiple choice, rating, and more. Returns the new form ID and shareable link.

fields.Name: CompanyID
fields.Description: The MemberJunction Company ID for credential lookup (optional - defaults to user's company)

fields.Name: Title
fields.Description: Title of the form

fields.Name: Fields
fields.Description: Array of field objects. Each field needs: type, title, and optional ref. Types: short_text, long_text, email, number, dropdown, multiple_choice, yes_no, rating, opinion_scale, date, phone_number, website, file_upload, payment, legal, matrix, ranking, picture_choice

fields.Name: Settings
fields.Description: Optional form settings object (e.g., {is_public: true, show_progress_bar: true})

fields.Name: Logic
fields.Description: Optional array of logic jump rules for conditional field display

fields.Name: HiddenFields
fields.Description: Optional array of hidden field names for URL parameters

fields.Name: ThemeID
fields.Description: Optional theme ID to apply to the form

fields.Name: WorkspaceID
fields.Description: Optional workspace ID where form should be created

fields.Name: Form
fields.Description: Complete created form object

fields.Name: FormID
fields.Description: The new form's ID

fields.Name: FormURL
fields.Description: Shareable URL for the form

fields.Name: FieldCount
fields.Description: Number of fields in the created form

fields.Name: Update Typeform
fields.Description: Updates an existing Typeform. WARNING: Uses PUT which replaces all form data - fields not included will be deleted. Set MergeWithExisting=true to safely update only specified properties while preserving others.

fields.Name: CompanyID
fields.Description: The MemberJunction Company ID for credential lookup (optional - defaults to user's company)

fields.Name: FormID
fields.Description: The Typeform form ID to update

fields.Name: MergeWithExisting
fields.Description: If true (default), fetches existing form and merges your changes. If false, replaces entire form with your data (DANGEROUS - will delete unspecified fields)

fields.Name: Title
fields.Description: New title for the form (optional if MergeWithExisting=true)

fields.Name: Fields
fields.Description: Array of field objects to replace all fields (required if MergeWithExisting=false)

fields.Name: Settings
fields.Description: Form settings to update (merged with existing if MergeWithExisting=true)

fields.Name: Logic
fields.Description: Array of logic jump rules (replaces existing logic)

fields.Name: HiddenFields
fields.Description: Array of hidden field names (replaces existing hidden fields)

fields.Name: ThemeID
fields.Description: Theme ID to apply to the form

fields.Name: Form
fields.Description: Complete updated form object

fields.Name: FormURL
fields.Description: Shareable URL for the form

fields.Name: FieldCount
fields.Description: Number of fields in the updated form

fields.Name: LastUpdated
fields.Description: Timestamp of last update
